skdetail:
Rated: Guidance Suggested. This skill contains: dynamic content.
Invocation Name: funny cookie
des:
~~Thanks for over 200 enables!!~~
Funny Cookie is an amazingly original fortune cookie simulator application, full of funny phrases written about many subjects, from family to dinosaurs. There are almost 199 phrases (198 to be exact) to collect and enjoy, with more coming soon with many updates in the future. Simply ask Alexa to open a Funny Cookie!

Disclaimer: This app contains crude humor, not all phrases are meant to be taken seriously.
priv: The developer reported that this skill does not collect personal information.
